            "title": "港股開市︱初段偏軟 恒指跌19點報26544點 滙控反彈1.65%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段偏軟，恒生指數開市報26544點，跌19點或0.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5737點，跌12點或0.22%；國企指數以9119點開市，跌15點或0.16%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股普遍再回，阿里巴巴(09988)開報159.8元，再跌0.37%；騰訊(00700)開報601元，跌1.48%；美團(03690)開報98.3元，跌0.2%；京東(09618)開報112.2元，微跌0.09%；小米(01810)開報36.02元，跌1.26%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於兩大藍籌國際金融股，滙控(00005)開報129.1元，升1.65%；友邦(01299)開報82.8元，跌0.18%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_HSBC-1.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240606_FI_source-web_HSBC-1.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上海石化(00338)發盈警，料去年由盈轉虧；該股今早開報1.45元，跌4.61%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">洛陽鉬業(03993)發12億美元1年期零息換股債，該股今早開報21.5元，跌1.29%。中集安瑞科(03899)折讓逾7%配股，該股今早開報10.31元，跌2.83%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國中免(01880)與DFS宣布大中華區零售業務收購協議，該股今早高開2.8%，以89.85元開市，創52周新高。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15595873-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c19%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126544%e9%bb%9e-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%881-65",
