            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報36607點，升19點，較上日現貨收市價26563點高水43點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5762點，升7點，高水12點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9150點，升5點，高水16點。</p>\n</div>",
